deal.highlightsHtml: <div data-content-type="html">Choose any movie at Regal! Enjoy great prices on tickets—including Premiere and Premium Format options—plus your favorite snack packs and popcorn. Whether it’s action, romance, cartoons, or horror, sit back and soak in the magic of the big screen!
deal.pitchHtml:
Highlights

  • Select from Premiere or Premium Format Tickets to match your movie-going style, from standard 2D to IMAX experiences

  • Elevate your movie experience with optional popcorn or a convenient snack pack available for purchase

  • Enjoy the newest releases at your convenience with nationwide access to over 400 Regal Cinemas

  • Immerse yourself in unforgettable storytelling with big screens, incredible surround sound, and plush seating

  • Give the gift of cinematic magic, perfect for family outings, date nights, or a fun escape

What To Expect

Choose from over 400 Regal Cinemas nationwide, open 365 days per year, and catch the newest movie releases with unmatched flexibility. Enhance your experience with optional popcorn or a snack pack for the ultimate movie viewing. Whether it’s a family outing, a date night (back row seats?), a friends’ get-together, or the perfect way to spend a rainy afternoon, Regal Movies is an escape into unforgettable storytelling.

Sink into the plush, spacious seats, designed for ultimate comfort, and let the immersive surround sound system transport you directly into the heart of the story. Whether you choose a Premiere ticket for a classic 2D film or upgrade to a Premium Format Ticket for the awe-inspiring spectacle of IMAX, 4DX, RPX, or ScreenX, every scene comes alive with stunning visuals. Enhance your cinematic journey with a generous, buttery box of freshly popped popcorn or a delightful snack pack, making your escape into fantastical storytelling truly complete.
Important Information — Popcorn and snack packs are sold separately.Additional fees apply for premium formats with Premiere Tickets.

Ticket Options

Premiere Ticket

Get big savings on your next trip to the movies! These Premiere Tickets are accepted for most standard 2D movies at any Regal theatre nationwide and never expire.

Premium Format Ticket

Love the full cinematic experience? These Premium Format Tickets are your all-access pass to any movie in any format—including IMAX, 4DX, RPX, and ScreenX—with no surprise fees at the box office. Just redeem and enjoy the show at any Regal theatre nationwide. These tickets never expire.

How It Works

1. Grab the Deal

Buy your Groupon first!

2. Go to the merchant's website or app or redeem your code in-person!

Select your movie, theatre, showtime, and seats.

3. Enter the code

In the payment section, enter your 15-digit Premiere eTicket code.

4. Enjoy the Experience!

FAQs

What's the difference between the Premiere Ticket and the Premium Format Ticket?

The Premiere Ticket is valid for standard 2D movies and may incur additional fees for premium formats like IMAX, 4DX, RPX, or ScreenX. The Premium Format Ticket is valid for any movie format, including these premium options, with no additional fees.

Do these movie tickets expire?

No, both Premiere and Premium Format Tickets never expire, offering you complete flexibility to enjoy a movie whenever you wish.

Are these tickets valid at all Regal Cinema locations?

Yes, your tickets are redeemable at any of the over 400 Regal Cinema locations nationwide, providing you with unmatched flexibility.

Are snacks like popcorn included with the movie tickets?

No, popcorn and snack packs are sold separately. You can choose to purchase a small popcorn or a snack pack which includes a snack-size popcorn, junior-size drink, and a Welch’s fruit snack.

How can I check movie showtimes and new releases?

You can check new releases, find movie information, and watch trailers on the Regal Cinemas website to plan your perfect movie outing.
